{"tid":417382,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我好想告鳩我中學個Miss","createTime":"2017-09-28T15:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T11:26:32.000Z","uid":5584,"like":15,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8a805b7dba7e3e454f3b6cc0d8daad0d5d069bec","tid":417382,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，我有交學費嫁（政府幫我交都算有交）<br />\n但又冇得自已揀Miss<br />\n條八婆自已都講到明係呃飯食<br />\n最撚慘年年升班咁啱又係佢教英文<br />\n<br />\n俾佢教左幾年英文，我發覺我真係冇進步過<br />\n係！我知道你地實會話我死蠢學唔識關人旦治bababa....<br />\n但重點係俾佢教過，我直頭對英文產生恐懼<br />\n<br />\n現在諗返起<br />\n真係好想告鳩佢瀆職<br />\n我知我想法真係好on 9<br />\n但真係唔想佢繼續為禍香港，誤人子弟<br />\n<br />\n有冇法律撚可以解答下，我可唔可以向佢民事索償？"},{"pid":"112ccfd05be79be0dac94d63aca7c87586f54909","tid":417382,"uid":30037,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"教畜真係害人一世"},{"pid":"ae3809d32d85071c94b5a198bb46bc1ac6f0be87","tid":417382,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"其實可以應該自學 上網搵文新聞自己睇<br />\n聽YouTube 練口音<br />\n好多brand 2 中中老師其實係廢"},{"pid":"335c7479d148c5f7c5bd3e7cd2166469f5337dd8","tid":417382,"uid":129043,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"自己廢 學唔識就話人呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7bb8393ba2e69c38aba0b20d6a2cd4a009f802","tid":417382,"uid":53672,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以應該自學 上網搵文新聞自己睇<br />\n聽YouTube 練口音<br />\n好多brand 2 中中老師其實係廢</blockquote><br />\n細個咁識諗就好"},{"pid":"d1f91f1c828b9f8cb5f2ac81f920388a305b4318","tid":417382,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:14:56.000Z","msg":"其實你可以就咁向教育局sd email投訴的"},{"pid":"3c1ce8143afd17d8f42ac22efdd6d2874bb744cf","tid":417382,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你可以就咁向教育局sd email投訴的</b