blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n所以其實宜家黎拗悔氣無用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條友現在應該繼續在呃飯食........<br />\n替辛辛學子慘......"},{"pid":"576859cc80873549ca51ebf2cc54aef187c02768","tid":417382,"uid":10894,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3547901fde5ec6601a7df51bd1f577420cf37acc","tid":417382,"uid":127454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊間</blockquote><br />\n唔自爆了<br />\n深水埗區</blockquote><br />\n深水埗係咁上下啦<br />\n垃圾俾留垃圾教</blockquote><br />\n英華呢ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8be153409229b5e062fdc9fcafa5c99c458d13f","tid":417382,"uid":4876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"SAME 學校有個教畜印度婆<br />\n我屌你老母正臭閪<br />\n自己唔識教書 派份英文新聞比半堂我地讀<br />\n半堂佢自己鳩UP抽啲字出黎講啲佢以為係解釋既解釋咁就一堂<br />\n又試過派份HANDOUT 睇一段15分鐘既新聞填返啲BLANK 咁就兩堂<br />\n要我地操卷 做PAPER3 PART B都要我地自己MARK 咁我要你做乜鳩?<br />\nSBA又比勁低分 唔好話係我廢先低分<br />\n係講緊全班平均無個有2字頭<br />\n人地學校SBA任做 做到你覺得夠高分為止 公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c873a25f9650b4e4d82f13da6615cb334d36ce3","tid":417382,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊間</blockquote><br />\n唔自爆了<br />\n深水埗區</blockquote><br />\n深水埗係咁上下啦<br />\n垃圾俾留垃圾教</blockquote><br />\n英華呢ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣人地問你英華係咩嚟"},{"pid":"e509a980f96e7915d04b7aa4ee791f7f555cc4d9","tid":417382,"uid":109082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母，我有交學費嫁（政府幫我交都算有交）<br />\n但又冇得自已揀Miss<br />\n條八婆自已都講到明係呃飯食<br />\n最撚慘年年升班咁啱又係佢教英文<br />\n<br />\n俾佢教左幾年英文，我發覺我真係冇進步過<br />\n係！我知道你地實會話我死蠢學唔識關人旦治<span style=\"color: red;\">blah blah blah (我估你係想咁寫？） </span><br />\n但重點係俾佢教過，我直頭對英文產生恐懼<br />\n<br />\n現在諗返起<br />\n真係好想告鳩佢瀆職<br />\n我知我想法真係好on 9<br />\n但真係唔想佢繼續為禍香港，誤人子弟<br />\n<br />\n有冇法律撚可以解答下，我可唔可以向佢民事索償？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文呢真係要靠自己下苦功的，唔好怕，睇多D。除左SCMP之外，譬如：BBC, Washington Post, The Guardian, CNN, Al Jazeera 甚至Huffington Post都好多野睇。  <br />\n<br />\n想有趣味d可以揀science 或者sports 黎睇，或者可以睇左中文的國際新聞再睇返呢d網站的英文報導，會易明d，又學到vocabulary 和sentence structure 。<br />\n<br />\n利申：中學英文老師都好廢，自己都努力掙扎中"},{"pid":"065c871dd045cf19b2014b1c394a8eefd20e0276","tid":417382,"uid":10894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"891d31effd9d7795be34d940ad907d8090deaece","tid":417382,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ae89baa2934f9c89b9cc286163d0a228d33a31f","tid":417382,"uid":126952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"老師都要負好大責任 因為自學要額外花時間<br />\n如果學校老師係廢 咁姐係浪費緊學生時間同資源"},{"pid":"de7e5f7aaf1610d62c451a58335f71f5ab026231","tid":417382,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"中三？"},{"pid":"3b340b7b0fb67f18801e6d9221cc2ea670360d1a","tid":417382,"uid":2716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"佢上堂係點教先"}]}